description: Network Subnet Trivia will help you learn how many available hosts are in a Class B and C subnet range.  You'll be asked how many hosts are in a slash twenty four, you'll need to answer with 254.

name: Network Subnet Trivia
shortDescription: Use Network Subnet Trivia to quickly learn the available hosts in class B and C subnets.
